query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('azure-active-directory',
'bit-manipulation',
'combinations',
'connection',
'css-grid',
'data-analysis',
'ftp',
'geometry',
'mercurial',
'navigation-drawer',
'python-imaging-library',
'resize',
'rss',
'scrollview',
'wordpress-plugin');
